Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:04.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}纠葛不清说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:10.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}轻轻地深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:19.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}愿这温柔的希望能持续到永久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:32.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}指尖描绘出的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否传递到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:38.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我愿今天也能继续欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:43.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}你明天也能充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}一定 一定
