Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,园丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油漆店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马车的修理工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没有刊登呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药剂师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我想找药剂师的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可惜我们这里不缺人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 你来当？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用外表来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让老主顾听到了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 真是对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前店里没法采集到的稀有药材都一应俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此 还有很多见都没见过的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问这些意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是老主顾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:52.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是前些日子嘱托的药种中的上等货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 虽然还年轻 但已经是一位宫廷药剂师了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 宫廷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 药剂师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侍奉宫廷的药剂师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在药剂师之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有拥有一流的知识和技术的才能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在克拉利涅斯王国只要优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人才都会得到支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个胸襟宽广的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉利涅斯 对医药学十分重视呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是宫廷药剂师的招募要点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在一年一度的招募考试合格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能作为见习进入威斯塔尔城工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为药剂师挑战一次也未尝不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过难度相当之高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我和近卫兵团的木木和光秀有会面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了 千殿下已经吩咐过我们您是来客了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 千殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在做什么？ 千
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做下运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因为公务不断 把身体给搞僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说办公到一半 偷偷溜出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多 也有段时间没见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算见面了呢 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千殿下 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会来这里 也就是找我有事吧 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你说过出城前要通知你一声 所以来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们两个 光秀那边帮我打个圆场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千殿下 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯特山？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡海之后的那座山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去那种地方做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说生长着很多药材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想自己去采来用作药学的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向城里的药店打听了几个药草的采摘地点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习？你不是已经是药剂师了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过以我现在的技术还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更加努力地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 明天就由我来送你去这片森林吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉利涅斯真是个好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里充满了魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红红的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 为什么是红红的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个姐姐的头发 红红的是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 别闹 吃东西要安静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和苹果一样看上去很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 妈妈 我想吃苹果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去买苹果吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苹果 苹果 红红的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为各种国家的人都从这里进出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掺杂着各种不同文化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是 千殿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好进到了不错的酒 意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就算了 改天再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在城里认识的酒店店主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 还拜托他准备过几次士兵的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千你为什么要从城里溜出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹巴伦的拉冀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是直接命令仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把想要的东西带进城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和自己的意愿相违就会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易想象了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚白雪你也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还隐藏着许多 我还不知道的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想看更多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解更多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的药需要上等的药草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上等的草药需要肥沃的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了这片土地 我就想了解这片土地的药草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开船咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要赶紧上船了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开船咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.14,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你找到好的药草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在天黑前会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了没 那个红发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是卖了的话想必是个不错的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来能做出不错的药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天的这次逃跑收获不小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么剩下的公务也有干劲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪也在努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪效果 真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫巳早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我在山脚跟你打过招呼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也能算做打招呼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然也不会找你搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你 你觉得一国的王子都没法得到的东西是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论进献到哪里 奖赏都是要多少有多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比方说如同天生就有宝石点缀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红发的姑娘…之类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是打算把我卖去哪里去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是进献了 进献
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有钱的好物之徒可是要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会想到干这种事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过等你头发再长长一点也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时把你放在我的身边也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 红发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 白雪不在家？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 今天早上还去给她送面包了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上屋里灯也没亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开饭了 你会吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天都在磨绳子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没其他出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说清楚这可是在山里 红发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算从这里出去了 你觉得一个人能逃走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有自己决定前往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间在这里耽搁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请你另寻他人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不继续逃了吗 红发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那么被抓也没什么能抱怨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 快起效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我点燃了带有麻痹作用的草药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短时间内身体的反应会变得迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你在这里慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚特意站在二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是因为害怕我上楼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜 到底为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那药也没什么效力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这山里你是比不过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这次给你跑了 下次还会被其他人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己献给贵族或者王族的话不是更安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅能得到保护 还能过上奢华的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得这个是不错的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢？红发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这种人生道路没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以由我来带你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊！你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说好一日游的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没事 没受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有保镖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还打算献上红发之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便讨下保镖这个活 以此谋生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然还考虑过这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这宅邸 是我家还是贵族时的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怪不得那么熟门熟路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能像野狗一样 偷偷住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家以前还算是挺辉煌的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的地位和家名 一瞬间就能被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你们这些穿着上等衣服 故作高雅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要失去了钱财就一无所有 只剩下一身污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不想继续过这种日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不择手段 想尽一切方法赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 你本该是个正合适的道具 红发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不关心你是怎么看待这个女孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪没有任何一点是作为道具而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来叫做白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许你叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊 是她的爸爸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 这家伙还有其他伙伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？不清楚 没有遇见其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的话 也能带着他下山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用遣送到城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给山脚下的官吏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡？你是什么人？叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千不是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉利涅斯第二王子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是白雪的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 请给他敷伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红发 你所说的自己想去的地方是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据官吏所说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫巳早的人和鼠窃狗偷之辈似乎没有联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我会注意自身安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 你在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一会儿就好看着我 就10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 很感激你来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然用言语远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5秒就行了 足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是有点生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是对你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不清 可能是对自己感到气愤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能知道城外的事情就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是知道了之后 可能会有我能做到事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 那个野猴子在被带走之前问你 你没答上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己决定前往的地方是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是我决定来这个国家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看 千在这个国家是如何生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能达成这个愿望的 就是我想前往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在那个地方 我也能看见你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 我也要向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的启程之国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启程之城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启程之路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算止步不前 这里也是我自己渴望的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定会扬起顺风助我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千的国家果然很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:24:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩会因有所期待而得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了目标 所以来向你报告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那个红发女孩就是千殿下的朋友…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是下贱的颜色
